### Health
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### List products
GET http://localhost:8000/products

### Filter by brand
GET http://localhost:8000/products?brand=Nike

### Filter by category
GET http://localhost:8000/products?category=Running

### Product detail
GET http://localhost:8000/products/1

### Chat request (requiere GEMINI_API_KEY válida)
POST http://localhost:8000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "user123",
  "message": "Hola, busco zapatos para correr talla 42"
}

### Chat history
GET http://localhost:8000/chat/history/user123?limit=10

### Clear history
DELETE http://localhost:8000/chat/history/user123
